<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Two matching <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">base</rs>s, with moulding at top and bottom; a: complete (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.625</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.90</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.615</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.48</measure>  × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.52</measure>) which is broken above and at left side. b: Four adjoining fragments, inscribed on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Severan; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.04-0.045</measure></p>
</div>
